title: War of the Roses: A Note in Her Makeup Bin
description: Audrey found something in her makeup bin after she got back from a vacation that shouldn't have been there so now she's questioning if her boyfriend Jesse is cheating on her.  He also used to untag himself in photos with girls when they first started dating so she's starting to calculate all the red flags in her head and needs to know what Jesse is up to.
